## Getting Started

### Run Locally

Clone the project

```bash
  git clone https://github.com/frontendship/website
```

Go to the project directory

```bash
  cd website
```

Change the branch

```bash
  git checkout development
```

Install dependencies

```bash
  npm install
```

Start the server

```bash
  npm run start
```

## Usage/Examples

```javascript
import Header from "../components/Header";

function App() {
  console.log("Hello world");
  return <Header />;
}
```
